Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}字幕转换助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.30,0:00:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}漂流的風找不到蹤跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}任何案件的推理都取決於心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}父母就是父母 小孩與其不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}超越小五郎 蘭的挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.71,0:00:13.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:14.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.85,0:00:21.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k234}正因為你和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.99,0:00:30.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喜好不同 腳程與表達的方式也大異其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.46,0:00:37.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如今我們在兩人的記憶中正在漸漸褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.43,0:00:45.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我摸索過 卻開始探尋其他人與未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.27,0:00:52.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我比自己想像的活的更堅強 追尋一種特別的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.41,0:00:56.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為難以應付的每一天所苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}true heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.69,0:01:07.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為了不再迷惑 請別鬆開你的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使是互相傷害的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.07,0:01:21.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我只是一直在迷惘的時空中找尋答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.68,0:01:27.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}朝著下一個舞台 you take you way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請抱緊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:38.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看不見的殺人機器之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k152}小蘭的初步推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好熱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.14,0:01:52.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}阿加巴裡是非常好的酒店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.17,0:01:54.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k203}但要走這麼斜的斜坡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.59,0:01:55.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k242}是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.41,0:01:57.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k82}剛剛碰到那個飛跑上來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}若再遇上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.73,0:02:01.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}我一定會好好的揍他一頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.54,0:02:03.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k181}到那時你可不要攔著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}是的 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.54,0:02:05.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.18,0:02:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k164}說來也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.90,0:02:08.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k72}你還有與新一聯絡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從那以後就沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k197}他還是在查那件案子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.91,0:02:17.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}到底那件事有什麼這麼有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.35,0:02:18.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}我真是搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.74,0:02:23.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}我有不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.89,0:02:31.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起 你們沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.07,0:02:38.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.61,0:02:39.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k154}什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來吉野小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k128}你是在富雅灣設計學校教書的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.34,0:02:50.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}是的 學校在靜岡那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}靜岡 很遙遠的地方嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 但時今天在回學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.79,0:03:00.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}途中突然想起忘記帶教科書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}然後就想打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k225}呀 我的先生也在這附近工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}他的公司就在這間酒店不遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想把他也一起叫來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}也好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}剛剛真的是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.97,0:03:18.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}突然間暈過去了，一睡不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.53,0:03:19.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}最近越來越頻繁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k138}老是不停的發作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你的身體到底那裡不舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k76}醫生說開心點就沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k258}我想可能與最近的天氣有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.42,0:03:32.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}最近不是突然熱得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k251}就是寒得入骨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}又也許 是因為每天進出靜岡、富岡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}兩地奔波疲勞過度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}倒不如我向學校請假幾天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.98,0:03:46.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}靜心休養一段時間就會好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.84,0:03:47.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}千穗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k189}這是我的丈夫吉野明夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.37,0:03:56.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}這是毛利蘭小姐和遷理子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我又突然失常了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k99}差點就撞倒這二位小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}又是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}那麼你們沒受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}沒事 一屁股蹲在地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.74,0:04:13.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且你們都已經賠禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.07,0:04:16.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}是嗎 真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼 你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.07,0:04:22.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}沒事 剛才休息了一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}他看起來好溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.68,0:04:30.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}我看我們還是先走一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.21,0:04:32.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k253}我去付款了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你們的家住在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}町下長南街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.49,0:04:42.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}啊 我們住的很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k161}我住在長南中街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.06,0:04:46.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}我們就在公園的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:46.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}斷層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.91,0:04:57.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}小心點 這裡有個斷層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸 你不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k138}什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.13,0:05:20.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}那是因為千穗小姐她老是頭暈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.43,0:05:23.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}且在那個斷層都不提醒要注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k283}如果不小心摔倒就大事不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}你不要把事情看得這麼重啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.58,0:05:31.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}男人嘛 就是那麼不拘小節的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.67,0:05:34.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是理子也碰到就馬上告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果是那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k94}絕對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.87,0:05:41.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k282}那像伙 是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒什麼 總然而之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.16,0:05:47.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k168}我就是覺得他們夫婦怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}一定要知道是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k198}那你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k163}當然是要找出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}她老是頭暈的原因啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.17,0:06:00.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}好 好 好 你可要自已小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k261}那就請隨便啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}我會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.66,0:06:10.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}小蘭她突然有這種幹勁來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.54,0:06:11.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}真是稀罕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}不過 這種事真是有點可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 我也可以一起去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.43,0:06:20.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}什麼 柯南你也跟我一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}那麼 把理子找來三人一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.64,0:06:27.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你喜歡吧 請幫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.00,0:06:27.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}添一碗飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.90,0:06:30.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}請你自便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我好可惱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.61,0:06:37.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}吉野家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.69,0:06:41.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}啊 好厲害 超漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}陽台裡到處都是花啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是好漂亮的家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}謝謝 這房間是結婚時特意買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}新婚家庭果然是不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}新房子真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.15,0:07:00.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}但是 一個月要交四千萬稅租
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過我們決定要為它而努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.30,0:07:08.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k134}不到最後都不會離開這間房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.56,0:07:08.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是 請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}謝謝 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k265}你本來應該是好好休息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k101}反正我也得早上起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k135}幫明夫做早點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.65,0:07:21.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}你的先生好溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 他不算是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k164}不過他很喜歡車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k164}他一看到喜歡的車型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}他就不惜巨款地購買了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}最近變得越來越瘋狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.54,0:07:31.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k136}所以他每天早上都會去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.06,0:07:33.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k152}車商走趟才會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.51,0:07:36.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k245}而我就在這段時間裡做早點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}我覺得有一點很奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k293}那為什麼你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}突然從靜岡那裡搬回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}那是因為明夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.44,0:07:50.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}他以前一直也跟我在學校教書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.98,0:07:54.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但後來聽說這邊的公司請人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.69,0:07:58.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且這邊工資高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.09,0:08:00.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雖然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}但是這不是很辛苦嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k201}每天要走這麼長的路回學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}說的也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}其實也可以坐電車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.62,0:08:13.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}但我不知道為什麼很喜歡開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你們不覺得自已開車很方便嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}不但可以自已控制時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}又可以喜歡上哪兒就上哪兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k252}是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}說起來也是 你們有投保的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.04,0:08:26.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k285}討厭 你們還只是高中生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.60,0:08:29.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.92,0:08:32.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}因為我先生是做保險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}跟他說多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}就好像自已也是做保險的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}啊 你真是一個好妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k272}不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.74,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k156}我聽先生說如果我死了後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.74,0:08:46.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k281}可以得到一千億的保險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一...一千億?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.62,0:08:52.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k177}有這麼多的保險金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.71,0:08:56.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}雖然很誇張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.15,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}這是我爸爸很久以前幫我買的保險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}但只有我死了後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}才能拿到這份保險金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k141}喂 可以給我一點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k228}也許可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一千億
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.96,0:09:10.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}請問 你老是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}突然暈過去的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}是從什麼時候開始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.47,0:09:22.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k202}也許是一個月前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.30,0:09:24.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一個月前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k128}一個月前不久是搬進來這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}半個月開始後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}那麼請問所患的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.98,0:09:31.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}衝擊後遺癥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k289}什麼 衝擊後遺癥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.83,0:09:40.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是 四苦八苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是 衝擊後遺癥啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是說有些人只要長時間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}跟那些綠色植物在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.36,0:09:50.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k152}他們就很容易生病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是因為綠色植物裡含有大量的甲醛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k149}你身為高中生應該知道這些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.65,0:09:56.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}那麼簡單的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.25,0:09:59.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}你別傻了 我當然知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但我想不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.34,0:10:04.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}那是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.30,0:10:06.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}因為我還未搬到這個家之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}我家裡也有種植物的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為我爸爸是個愛好植物的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.75,0:10:15.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k281}所以我從小習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.43,0:10:18.07,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.07,0:10:18.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k64}不應該是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k76}我們還是查清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}到底是發生什麼事好些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k281}雖然 理子你好像認識一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k236}專門幫人清洗甲醛味的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.28,0:10:32.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 爸爸也許有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼我們馬上找他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}千穗小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.89,0:10:38.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}不如讓那些人來幫你清除味道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}蘭 你今天怎麼變得這麼怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.39,0:10:54.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到底是發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.27,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.87,0:10:58.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}那是因為小蘭姐姐感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.99,0:11:01.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k112}千穗姐姐的先生行為很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.83,0:11:05.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}他對千穗小姐的表現有點假惺惺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼 真的是這樣的 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到底是什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k248}首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.29,0:11:17.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}明夫是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.53,0:11:21.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}特意從靜岡搬來富岡居住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.18,0:11:24.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的只是因為這邊的薪水多一點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.92,0:11:25.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還是有別的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k66}千穗小姐決對不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.94,0:11:31.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}辭掉設計的工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.38,0:11:33.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}啊 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k225}千穗小姐每天都要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.11,0:11:38.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}往返一段很長的路程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果就在途中她暈了過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.80,0:11:55.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的 你想的太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.97,0:12:01.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k144}住在那裡對明夫來真的很方便啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當然是住在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}但是 他們也可以住得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.99,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}離靜岡近一點的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看還是有很多的疑點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.39,0:12:18.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我們一定要把事情弄清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k247}雖然蘭的推理是很表面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}但也真的存在很多的疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到底問題在那裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.01,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}想不透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.91,0:12:38.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個是用來清除甲醛味道的儀器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.99,0:12:41.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還有我希望在我們進行工作期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.65,0:12:46.06,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}請大家離開屋外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 那麼拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.14,0:12:50.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}好了 我們開始工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}不聽你們說也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k221}原來千穗經常暈倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.31,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k172}是和那些植物有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.31,0:13:00.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}這次真是感謝你們的幫忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}希望可以一次徹底清除它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.24,0:13:08.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼 我去散步時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}順便買些蛋糕回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.97,0:13:16.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.97,0:13:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他真是一個散步癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.62,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我也要去散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}柯南 你要早點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k264}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個客人真是錢多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.26,0:14:09.22,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}他每次都來買高級車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.22,0:14:15.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼 2500萬 太厲害了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.43,0:14:17.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看經過這次洗刷後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.75,0:14:22.48,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}四年內不會有甲醛味了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我們運用了BBN系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.88,0:14:28.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}把甲醛全部清除了 請放心居住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}那就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.93,0:14:35.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k165}這間房間是完全安全的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k128}以後我不會再出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.89,0:14:41.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k132}什麼衝擊後遺癥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一直以來辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k176}你以後可以安心居住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.26,0:14:46.94,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k256}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.91,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}到底是什麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k281}事情一定另有原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我不是早就說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.54,0:15:05.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}你做事就老是鑽牛角尖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.22,0:15:10.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還是我想多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.11,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.11,0:15:15.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k62}是名偵探毛利小五郎的女兒嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你可不要隨便丟我的臉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.84,0:15:23.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k193}自尊心重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k224}以後怎麼當別人的妻子啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.86,0:15:29.76,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要像那傢伙一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k229}我根本就做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.83,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}小蘭姐姐的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k158}也有點錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.83,0:16:05.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天我在明夫到過的車商問過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.74,0:16:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}明夫他今天買了一部二千五百萬的跑車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.97,0:16:14.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}二千五百萬 他從那裡來錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.23,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}莫非是千穗小姐的保險金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.37,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k232}難道是為千穗小姐的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.97,0:16:25.16,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}聽說他們的銀行的戶口裡還有六千萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.99,0:16:30.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但他是怎麼向千穗小姐下毒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}莫非是食物裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.01,0:16:37.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k276}但是食物是由千穗小姐親手做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.21,0:16:38.69,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}到底是從下手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}如果你在這裡就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.89,0:16:56.51,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}你一定可以解決千穗小姐的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呢 新一我該怎麼做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.02,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}事情還真是很刺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}當初蘭說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.68,0:17:10.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.43,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}莫非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k157}難道千穗小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}是的 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.28,0:17:22.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}第一次跟千穗小姐談話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.92,0:17:26.12,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她是怎樣告訴你們她老是頭暈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.36,0:17:28.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k152}我想可能與最近的天氣有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.56,0:17:33.85,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k268}最近不是突然熱得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}就是寒得入骨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.95,0:17:39.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k206}又也許 是因為每天進出靜岡、富岡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}兩地奔波疲勞過度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k233}倒不如我向學校請假幾天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.78,0:17:47.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}靜心休養一段時間就會好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.65,0:17:51.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}如果沒有什麼特別的原因的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.71,0:17:55.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}有誰喜歡住在離工作地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k124}這麼遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}而且一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.71,0:17:59.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k116}每天都是這麼疲勞的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k84}身體怎麼會好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.04,0:18:04.04,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k249}你這樣說也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.94,0:18:07.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}我看千穗小姐老是頭暈的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k244}應該不是家裡的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在別的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.77,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k257}是在靜岡的設計學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.17,0:18:17.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}又也許在去的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k272}什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}莫非是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.98,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}第二天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.98,0:18:28.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k86}那我去散步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.78,0:18:30.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}今天早上吃飯好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}好呀 我的肚子好餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那早點就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 你們怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.20,0:19:25.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}吉野先生 那口袋的東西是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.94,0:19:29.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 這個嘛 只是香水而以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.54,0:19:33.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是最新的檀花味的香水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.07,0:19:38.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這些話請留著對警察說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.45,0:19:39.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k148}剛剛你所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k137}千穗小姐已全部聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.58,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}千穗小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.98,0:19:48.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}千穗小姐連做夢也想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.64,0:19:50.26,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k266}自已這麼心愛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.26,0:19:53.87,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k162}竟然在車上噴甲醛來害她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.87,0:19:57.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怪不得千穗小姐在家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.67,0:20:05.44,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這一段時間裡病並沒有好轉過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.88,0:20:12.49,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}千穗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.13,0:20:16.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.15,0:20:33.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}經過警察的調查後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.31,0:20:39.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k216}發現原來吉野他一直虧空公款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.88,0:20:50.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他是以那部二千五佰萬的車來做補償
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.99,0:21:19.29,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不知道　該用什麼話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.74,0:21:26.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才能告訴你我真正的感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.44,0:21:35.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從那時起　不知過了多少季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.39,0:21:41.64,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雖然時間無情地流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.36,0:21:49.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你卻總是　微笑地陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.04,0:21:59.39,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我沒對你說出口的  至今還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.54,0:22:04.36,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Secret of my heart 請你不要懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.49,0:22:10.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}無論何時　只要還有少許未來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.66,0:22:15.54,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真相　是緊握在手中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.69,0:22:22.19,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I can't say 請給我點時間  I'm waiting for a chance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.74,0:22:31.57,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼 千穗小姐已把那房子賣掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.95,0:22:32.35,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.35,0:22:36.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k40}而且她辭了工作到很遠的地方工作去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.05,0:22:38.47,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.97,0:22:41.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}很有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.60,0:22:46.68,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k263}切口千穗 他們已離婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.10,0:22:50.24,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的 女生真是善變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.24,0:22:53.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看以後要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.55,0:22:55.81,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k231}小蘭也快要變成那樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.01,0:22:58.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k246}真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.13,0:23:01.82,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}千穗小姐叫小蘭你也要好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.74,0:23:05.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看你還是掛著那個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.66,0:23:09.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.95,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}但是 雖然他不在我的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.17,0:23:16.79,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我好像感覺到他就在我的身邊一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.95,0:23:21.08,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊 原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.08,0:23:24.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}希望新一也有這種感覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.00,0:23:28.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.88,0:23:33.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}那傢伙冷血的一定不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.99,0:23:35.41,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.95,0:23:38.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}不如我們去吃點好東西吧
